# Atlas Architecture

## Core modules

- `app/` – Next.js application screens
- `components/` – shared UI
- `lib/types.ts` – domain model
- `lib/storage.ts` – local persistence
- `public/manifest.webmanifest` – PWA metadata

## v0.1 storage

Data are stored in `localStorage`.

Next step: move to IndexedDB for larger offline datasets and video metadata.
